$ Registry: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\ProductOptions

This key specifies which variant of Windows is booted.

{ ProductType #ProductType
 
 table { ll
   ~Value~   ☰  ~Windows edition~
    WinNt    ☰   Windows client
    LanmanNT ☰   → Windows/versions/Server[Windows server] - domain controller
    ServerNT ☰   → Windows/versions/Server[Windows server] - server only
 table }

   See also the functions
     • `VerifyVersionInfo`
     • `RtlGetVersion`
     • `RtlVerifyVersionInfo`

}
{ ProductSuite

  This value contains a cached copy of the data in → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/spp/store/2_0/tokens_dat

}
